{"tid":195082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講下身邊啲悲觀撚","createTime":"2017-04-10T11:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T11:34:27.000Z","uid":75955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e34a6f81c7b633666a365cfe200cdef9797b19ff","tid":195082,"uid":75955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"有冇人身邊有啲悲觀撚做fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時小事大事失敗左都係用：因為我垃圾 我黑仔 註定係咁架啦 嚟做結論<br />\n剩係focus喺唔開心嘅事 好事成功嘅野反而唔重視<br />\n但你有問題個時搵佢 佢又好細心比好多意見你 甚至件事嘅原因同解決方法都一一幫你諗埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反佢地咁諗就完全幫唔到手 改變唔到佢地負面嘅諗法<br />\n有冇人身邊有呢啲fd 或者自己就係悲觀撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該點先幫到佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}